<%= link_to image_tag("hen_party_decorations.jpg", :alt => "Hen party decorations", :class => "header-img"), resources_path %>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row resources">
        <article role="main">

        	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
             	<h3>Find everything you need to make your hen party extra special. Here you can access games templates, food and drinks recipes and recommended purchases. You can also bookmark items and come back to them later.</h3>
           </div>  

			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 item">
				<%= link_to image_tag("cocktails.jpg", :alt => "Cocktails", :class => "header-img"), resources_path %>
				<h2><%= link_to "Food and drink recipes", resources_path %></h2>
				<p>Prepare your own food and drinks with fun twists or classic mixtures.</p>
				<p class="att">The above image is available on CC license. By Karen - <a target="blank" href="https://flic.kr/p/5atRuu">https://flic.kr/p/5atRuu</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 item">
				<%= link_to image_tag("games.jpg", :alt => "Mr & Mrs Game template", size: "200"), resources_path %>
				<h2><%= link_to "Personalised templates", resources_path %></h2>
				<p>Personalise and print templates for games, t-shirts and invitations.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4 item">
				<%= link_to image_tag("accessories.jpg", :alt => "Shopping", size: "200"), resources_path %>
				<h2><%= link_to "Recommended Purchases", resources_path %></h2>
				<p>A house needs decorations, a hen needs accessories and the party needs a theme. Here's a list of what to buy and where to get it.</p>
			</div>

        </article>
    </div>
</div>